text=PmWiki has the capability of classifying pages into groups of related pages.  [[WikiWord]]s act as [[links]] between pages of the same group; to create a link to a wiki page in another group, you use [@[[GroupName.WikiWord]]@] or [@[[GroupName/WikiWord]]@] to create the link.²²By default, the [[RecentChanges]] page of each group shows only the pages that have changed within that group; the [[Main.AllRecentChanges]] page shows all pages that have changed in all groups.²²To list all the groups in a site, try the markup [@(:pagelist fmt=group:)@].²²Creating a new group is as easy as [[CreatingNewPages]]; simply edit an existing page to include a [[link(3,36

